    <siteMapNode title="Comprehensive Cancer Screening in Dubai by Dermatology, Laser hair Removal, Mole Removal Dental Cosmocare Medical Center" description="Screening can help doctors find and treat several types of cancer early, before they cause symptoms. Early detection is important because when abnormal tissue or cancer is found early, it may be easier to treat. By the time symptoms appear, cancer may have begun to spread and be harder to treat." url="~/comprehensive-cancer-screening.html"/>
