    <siteMapNode title="Hyperhidrosis (Excessive Sweating) Treatment by Specialist Doctor in Dubai | Dermatology, Laser hair Removal, Mole Removal Dental Cosmocare Medical Center" description="There are many treatment options for sufferers of hyperhidrosis. At our clinic we will help you determine what method is best for you. There are several types of oral medications used to control hyperhidrosis. Anticholinergics, for example, block nerve impulses to sweat glands, thereby blocking sweat output." url="~/excess-sweating.html"/>
